perPlantCosts.title: Price per plant
perPlantCosts.note: Enter the average per plant costs from your supplier or nursery. If you don't know, use the default provided.

perPlantCosts.title: Labour cost per plant
perPlantCosts.note: The average cost of labour required to get a plant in the ground. Use this to budget in time taken to plant each plant. Ask for a per-plant rate if using a contractor and enter it here. The default is an average estimated cost to use if you are carrying out the planting yourself.

perPlantCosts.title: Other costs per plant
perPlantCosts.note: This value includes the costs involved in any other per plant item or requirement e.g. stakes, plant protectors. Note that maintenance costs are covered separately on a per feature basis in the planning section.
